如果淨係針對 function 同 string 互轉，其中一個方法可以用 <code>f1 = String( function() {...} )</code> 做 encode 然後 <code>new Function(&quot;return &quot; + f1)()</code> 來還原<br />
<br />
例子：<br />
<pre><code data-type="js">const funcs = {
    a: function() {
        console.log(&quot;a func&quot;)
    },
}

// encode
let outFunc = {}
for (func in funcs) {
    outFunc[func] = String(funcs[func])
}
let j = JSON.stringify(outFunc)

// decode
let inFunc = {}
for (func in outFunc) {
    inFunc[func] = new Function(&quot;return &quot; + outFunc[func])()
}
inFunc['a']() // call</code></pre><br />
如果你個 object 入面有唔係 function type 既 variable 要自己做返 checking

睇返 MDN 有個 function 叫 uneval 但目前 obsolete 咗<br />
<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/uneval" data-sr-url="https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Fdocs%2FWeb%2FJavaScript%2FReference%2FGlobal_Objects%2Funeval&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1apJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=a2ad30c4" data-auto-link target="_blank">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/uneval</a><br />
<br />
搵到有個 gist 可以做到相近既野，可以用 eval 來還原返<br />
<a href="https://gist.github.com/cho45/242072" data-sr-url="https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgist.github.com%2Fcho45%2F242072&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1apJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=da757679" data-auto-link target="_blank">https://gist.github.com/cho45/242072</a><br />
<pre><code data-type="js">// import uneval gist: https://gist.github.com/cho45/242072
const ans = {
    a: async function(b) {
        console.log(&quot;a func&quot;, b)
        return b
    },
    b: function(b) {
        console.log(&quot;b func&quot;, b)
        return b
    },
    c: &quot;c val&quot;
}
const ansStr = uneval(ans)

const ans2 = eval(ansStr)
ans2.a(&quot;test&quot;).then(r =&gt; {
    console.log(&quot;async result&quot;, r)
})
ans2.b(&quot;test&quot;)
console.log(ans2.c)

/* output
a func test
b func test
c val
async result test
*/</code></pre>

